videos.description: Joshua Langord pulls up from deep for a 3-pointer early in the first half, scoring his first points in his first game since December 29, 2018.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (MSU's Langford drills 3 for first bucket in two years) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: MSU's Langford drills 3 for first bucket in two years

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo and Rob Murphy honor legendary coach John Thompson with a towel over their shoulders in the Spartans' season opener.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Izzo, MSU coaches honor John Thompson) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Izzo, MSU coaches honor John Thompson

videos.description: Michigan State's Joshua Langford drives in from the corner, bodies multiple Eastern Michigan defenders and gets a tough shot to fall off the glass in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Langford doesn't hesitate with smooth kiss off the glass for two) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Langford doesn't hesitate with smooth kiss off the glass for two

videos.description: Marcus Bingham Jr. comes from behind and denies Bryce McBride on the glass.

videos.description: Marquette transfer Joey Hauser shows up in the second half, throwing down a powerful two-handed dunk for Michigan State.

videos.headline: Hauser drives through the lane for two-handed slam

videos.description: Mady Sissoko swats an Eastern Michigan shot attempt into the stands much to his teammates' delight.
